  not_derived_from:
    - "CPython source code"
    - "any proprietary source"
  notes:
    - "Wave 675 (st3421): __hash__, __eq__, __lt__ dict-presence checks for struct.Struct."
    - "Theme: __hash__/__eq__/__lt__ dict-presence (hash(x), x==y, x<y)."
    - "All values False — struct.Struct is a C-level type (_struct.Struct); it does not define __hash__, __eq__, or __lt__ in its own __dict__."
    - "struct.Struct instances represent compiled format strings — they are binary format descriptors and do not override hash/eq/lt at the class level."
    - "All values are False — struct.Struct has no hash/eq/lt conversion defined in its own __dict__."
    - "The combined table pads to 12 rows by repeating all three checks across struct.Struct."
    - "All values verified with Python 3.14.4 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-13."
  created_at: "2026-04-13"
error_model: python_exceptions

